2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses the limitations of CNN-based methods in image steganalysis and proposes a new framework to overcome these limitations. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with steganography in JPEG images, which is a multimedia format. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses iterative adversarial examples to update the embedding cost, which is a machine learning technique. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses adversarial examples to improve the security performance of steganography, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence.
